Package: bangladesh
Title: Provides ready to use shapefiles for geographical map of Bangladesh
Description: The purpose of this package is to provide ready to use shapefiles
    for different administrative regions of Bangladesh (e.g. Division, District, Upazila, Union).
    Usually it is difficult to plot choropleth maps for Bangladesh in R. This package will help
    users to draw thematic maps of administrative regions of Bangladesh as it comes with the 
    sf objects for the boundaries and regions' names in English. It also provides some functions
    that allows users to easily get specific area maps and to get center coordinates for regions. 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
